            <para>
                <emph type="boldundersc">WIRING INFORMATION:</emph>
            </para>
            <para>The circuit ratings are as follows: headlamp hi beam 20 amp, headlamp low beam 20 amp, left turn 10
                amp, right turn 10 amp and park 15 amp. Since the auxiliary park and turn current is shared with vehicle
                lighting current, make sure the added lighting does not exceed the stated current rating for each
                circuit. All circuit protection is internal to the ESC.
            </para>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>If the plow lights are turned on without the lights being connected, the ESC will log a
                        headlamp fault code.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
